   With: IRAN-WOMEN and IRAN-GO.
</P>
<P>
   TRAVEL-COLUMN (Undated) _ An arbitrary list of 10 destinations I
aim to visit again. And 10 to which I yearn to travel. I have fond
memories of such places as the Oregon coast to Washington, D.C. And
I hope to visit such places as Cooperstown, N.Y., and Cape Cod,
Mass. By HARRY SHATTUCK.
</P>
<P>
   NAPLES (Naples, Italy) _ The only Napoleans we encountered were
friendly. No one tried to pick our pockets, hold a knife to our
throats or otherwise live up to Naples' frightful reputation. I
began to wonder whether all those stories were circulated by locals
who didn't want tourists monopolizing the restaurants. By JOHN
FLINN.
