<P>
   MILAN-MENS-FASHION (Undated) _ Review of the rest of the men's
wear collections in Milan. By Constance White.
</P>
<P>
   PARIS-MENS-FASHION (Undated) _ Review of the men's fashion shows
in Paris. By Constance White.
</P>
<P>
   PATTERNS-FASHION (Undated) _ News and notes on fashion. By
Constance White.
</P>
<P>
   BY-DESIGN-FASHION (Undated) _ A short feature on pareos. By
Anne-Marie Schiro.
</P>
