<DATE_TIME> 1998-07-06 15:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2153 &Cx1f; sci-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BRODY-HEALTH-ART-NYT &LR;      07-06 1229
