By Richard Sandomir.
</P>
<P>
   EAST-GERMANY-DRUGS (Paris) _ A former East German sports doctor
has admitted in a Berlin court that he handed out anabolic steroids
for use by young female swimmers, the first formal confession of
such practices by an official of the Communist state that once
churned out gold-medal winning athletes with bizarre consistency.
By Roger Cohen.
</P>
