<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MEANS-COLUMN-1STLD-WRITETHRU-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CAMPAIGN FEVER 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (EDs: CORRECTS spelling of ``inaugural'' in 3d graf)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By MARIANNE MEANS  
 c.1998 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ It turns out President Clinton is still a Democrat,
no matter what you thought.
</P>
<P>
   Well, for the coming campaign season, anyway.
</P>
<P>
   Two years ago, he ignored his fellow Democrats and campaigned
