   Photos are available on Wieck, Newscom or through e-mail.
</P>
<P>
   1. STOP HEADACHES ... LIKE MAGIC. From Prevention with art. Get
rid of tension headaches _ fast and for good. Here, some
do-it-yourself remedies. (slugged: BC-RODALE-COVER-NYTSF).
</P>
<P>
   2. HEALTH BRIEFS. From Prevention with art. Bimonthly aspirin
booster; beat hypertension at any age and any stage; no more
